                <h2>Why Visit</h2>
                <p>The beloved seasonal park on Penn’s Landing offers visitors the chance to lounge on colorful hammocks, enjoy Philly-inspired eats on floating barges, cool off with craft brews in the beer garden and play games – bocce, shuffleboard and more – along a waterfront boardwalk.</p>
                <p>Day or night, Spruce Street Harbor Park offers excellent options for outdoor recreation and is free and open to the public in the spring through fall.</p>
